{"tid":1460012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我好擔心，係咪要有人死先得？","createTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T01:23:03.000Z","uid":37247,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4484bb50d8428931ce8f1c6b2a695b794051bd1","tid":1460012,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:24.000Z","msg":"Sorry用d咁嘅標題引大家入黎<br />\n我係一個而家搭緊車返工嘅打工仔<br />\n星期日晚太過悲憤瞓唔着<br />\n尋日就請咗假入機場<br />\n但係公司department入面個個都係同路人<br />\n但係都冇商量過共識<br />\n我擔心嘅係，係咪好多人都好似我咁淨係得尋日一日入去塞機場<br />\n癱瘓一日發洩完今日又過返正常生活？<br />\n醫護界已經打響頭炮無限期罷工<br />\n點解仲未見其他行業出黎罷工？<br />\n無人講罷工，咁到底今日會有幾多人入機場<br />\n癱唔癱瘓到機場。。。<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋得第一日成功，之後幾日都失敗<br />\n咁下一個爆發點係咩？<br />\n係咪要見到自己人比警黑打死先有大罷工？<br />\n<br />\n如果你同我一樣而家返緊公司<br />\n唔緊要<br />\n記得同你上次有份一齊罷工嘅同事傾下<br />\n813，繼續一齊入機場！"},{"pid":"cd9c79ee6e255065c444ec7b3ae0e217d891ae58","tid":1460012,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:58.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b9568e611f12820709d69cfdbb09f2dcd01b3c07","tid":1460012,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:41:10.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"595b19fb9c8460b0645f74378227a9e9fa981b54","tid":1460012,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"a9c46d239a5dc0b31c20491ac61d4e62dc3067a4","tid":1460012,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:41:30.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"2372ff6246e620fbe2814ad4aa33a396740bec61","tid":1460012,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:42:14.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"4de8b86c4f4d7f2cc0b1ebfb7fb2cf70a3fee0d8","tid":1460012,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:42:25.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"3432f425e14ecd6835d76e2b22ee697ffd8ec23e","tid":1460012,"uid":37247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00